Package: OCepi
Type: Package
Title: Collection of Common Data Cleaning Tools for Epidemiologists
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Eric", "Shearer", , "ericshearer@me.com", role = c("aut","cre","cph"))
  )
Description: Collection of data cleaning fuctions that strives to standardized the approach in the mundane data wrangling tasks. Made specifically with California epidemiologists in mind, these methods can be applied broadly in many contexts.
